{"tid":1001651,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"90後心中嘅兩大歌王都老啦","createTime":"2019-01-30T10:04:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T16:05:44.000Z","uid":49781,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d3f83b24fbd790d55b3c23b28cd6cae6709f9bb0","tid":1001651,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T10:04:44.000Z","msg":"<strong>陳奕迅 (44歲)</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ee55pak.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEe55pak.gif&h=0fcdcf99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我們萬歲MV</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>古巨基 (46歲)</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RQeJVhD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRQeJVhD.gif&h=54659783&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">亂世情侶MV</span><br />\n<br />\n兩位嘅經典歌真係撐起四分之三個00年代樂壇，「薯條鬥傑青」、「怪獸鬥Human」更令我哋呢班樂迷好Enjoy好投入，宜家兩位都唔再玩香港小圈子分獎禮啦。<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">如果遲啲兩位可以合作出首合唱歌、玩個音樂會，完我哋呢班Fans嘅心願就好啦</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3kXCZL7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3kXCZL7.jpg&h=07765fa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n古巨基、陳奕迅、李克勤曾被稱四大天王後嘅「樂壇三劍俠」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0aeJVkR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0aeJVkR.jpg&h=d424b409&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然係2012年頭陳奕迅因為想娛記停止<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">製造</span></strong>佢同古巨基之間所謂嘅鬥爭「新聞」，假意串古巨基不是強敵(而是朋友)，引來各方不滿 (呢件事之後的確冇人再敢寫陳奕迅鬥古巨基嘅「新聞」)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xUG0XAQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxUG0XAQ.jpg&h=0e1aaa0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但二人多次在公開場合表示互相欣賞對方，關係唔錯，只係因為公司不同(甚至對立)而甚少合作<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=drqUci0fPTE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdrqUci0fPTE&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfB8LrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=4a8afac2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=drqUci0fPTE</a><br />\n唯一一次(錄音上嘅)合作係1996年出嘅《兩個阿伯殺手》，黃偉文填詞"},{"pid":"024a918ffde25c01c0abd2364649fa85ba615477","tid":1001651,"uid":196924,"like":14,"dislike":20,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T10:11:15.000Z","msg":"呢位古生邊撚到歌王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13342de4fa1a65d473476d92792f885072d8edc1","tid":1001651,"uid":49781,"like":15,"dislike":5,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"024a918ffde25c01c0abd2364649fa85ba615477","tid":1001651,"uid":196924,"like":14,"dislike":20,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T10:11:15.000Z","msg":"呢位古生邊撚到歌王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T10:13:18.000Z","msg":"你00後?"},{"pid":"599e2b49768822451143817bf28f6633d693fa59","tid":1001651,"uid":36911,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T10:14:53.000Z","msg":"咁屈就陳生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"488d9920b10c573581a79e5427274862ced5f860","tid":1001651,"uid":46014,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T10:22:50.000Z","msg":"呢兩個嘅話<br />\n我諗你應該係90尾"},{"pid":"2d2cdfb469e36f9a4201e7217915446e534fda61","tid":1001651,"uid":5591,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T10:33:26.000Z","msg":"講左好多次，明明宋禮係同牛華學友差唔多時間出道/出碟，而家成日比人屈做咩三劍俠！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2906fa8edb8c53a1102b24892b67e90ac351a1f","tid":1001651,"uid":95508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T10:34:04.000Z","msg":"46<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d04fbae42e3a4c7857c9dfaa51bc3d36145adc26",